  "name": "Hearth of Moonlight and Shadow",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "icons/magic/nature/moon-crescent.webp",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 6th level, home can be wherever you are. During a short or long rest, you can invoke the shadowy power of the Gloaming Court to help guard your respite. At the start of the rest, you touch a point in space, and an invisible, 30-foot-radius sphere of magic appears, centered on that point. Total cover blocks the sphere.</p>\n<p>While within the sphere, you and your allies gain a +5 bonus to Dexterity (Stealth) and Wisdom (Perception) checks, and any light from open flames in the sphere (a campfire, torches, or the like) isn't visible outside it.</p>\n<p>The sphere vanishes at the end of the rest or when you leave the sphere.</p>\n<section class=\"secret\">\n<p><em>Note: Edit your Stealth and Perception skills and add +5 to the Check Bonus field.</em></p>\n</section>",
